%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20front-line%20NATO%20forces%20are%20training%20to%20operate%20and%20survive%20one%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20war's%20deadliest%20threats%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224470%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22First%20Person%20View%20(FPV)%20drone%20controlled%20via%20fibre%20optics%20is%20seen%20during%20a%20test%20flight.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683d6cf7ca50259add4d6cd8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223199%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDrones%2C%20especially%20those%20controlled%20by%20fiber-optic%20cables%2C%20have%20emerged%20as%20a%20key%20threat%20in%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3EMykhaylo%20Palinchak%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Ukraine%20war%20has%20seen%20a%20proliferation%20of%20drones%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENATO%20allies%20are%20closely%20watching%20the%20developing%20drone%20war%20and%20learning%20from%20the%20battlefield%20tactics.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMilitary%20leaders%20from%20Finland%20and%20Poland%20told%20BI%20how%20their%20forces%20are%20training%20with%20drones.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFinland%20and%20Poland%20%E2%80%94%20two%20front-line%20NATO%20allies%20that%20share%20borders%20with%20Russia%20%E2%80%94%20are%20experimenting%20with%20new%20ways%20of%20war%20using%20drones%2C%20military%20leaders%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20noting%20the%20radical%20changes%20unfolding%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECol.%20Matti%20Honko%2C%20the%20commanding%20officer%20of%20Finland's%20Guard%20Jaeger%20Regiment%2C%20said%20that%20one%20of%20the%20main%20lessons%20from%20Ukraine%20is%20that%20there%20is%20increased%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrones-watching-soldiers-shows-future-wars-scary-us-army-officer-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etransparency%20on%20the%20modern%20battlefield%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20of%20drones%