said%20this%20also%20includes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrones-becoming-more-lethal-army-must-be-ready-fight-officer-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecounter-drone%20and%20other%20defensive%20measures%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20should%20be%20taken.%20He%20declined%20to%20go%20into%20specifics%20about%20the%20training%20scenarios%20but%20stressed%20that%20they%20are%20not%20yet%20fully%20integrated%20into%20everyday%20drills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECpl.%20Jimi%20J%C3%A4rnberg%2C%20a%20soldier%20of%20the%203rd%20Jaeger%20Company%2C%20a%20unit%20of%20the%20Finnish%20Army's%20Pori%20Brigade%2C%20told%20BI%20during%20Lively%20Sabre%20that%20uncrewed%20systems%20are%20excellent%20surveillance%20tools%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20avoid%20exposing%20humans%20to%20harm%20when%20gathering%20intel%2C%20but%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-air-defender-guns-arent-enough-kill-russian-drones-anymore-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUkraine%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20highlights%20the%20danger%20of%20turning%20drones%20into%20bombs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20type%20of%20weapon%20%E2%80%94%20a%20cheap%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-military-isnt-ready-drones-potential-biggest-threat-next-battlefield-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecommercially%20available%20quadcopter%3C%2Fa%3E%20drone%20that%20carries%20a%20small%20explosive%20payload%2C%20for%20example%20%E2%80%94%20is%20omnipresent%20on%20the%20battlefield%20in%20Ukraine.%20Both%20Kyiv%20and%20Moscow%20use%20them%20to%20deliver%20precision%20strikes%20on%20enemy%20troops%2C%20armored%20vehicles%2C%20and%20trenches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrones%20are%20widely%20recognized%20as%20the%20future%20of%20war.%20In%20Ukraine%2C%20they%20are%20proving%20deadlier%20than%20artillery%2C%20with%20reports%20from%20the%20front%20lines%20indicating%20they%20are%20responsible%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-ground-robots-hit-russia-more-explosives-flying-drones-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eroughly%2080%25%20of%20Russian%20front-line%20losses%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20the%20world%20watches%20these%20developments%2C%20Finland%20is%20not%20alone%20in%20recognizing%20the%20significance%20of%20this%20threat%20and%20integrating%20new%20drone%20tactics%20into%20its%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrig.%20Gen.%20Michal%20Strzelecki%2C%20the%20commander%20of%20Poland's%206th%20Airborne%20Brigade%2C%20which%20participated%20in%20Lively%20Sabre%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20his%20forces%20are%20also%20experimenting%20with%20this%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225671%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20this%20photo%20provided%20by%20Ukraine's%2024th%20Mechanized%20Brigade%20press%20service%2C%20servicemen%20prepare%20the%20drone%20%26quot%3BKazhan%26quot%3B%20that%20delivers%20supply%20and%20carry%20heavy%20bombs%2C%20on%20the%20front%20line%20near%20Chasiv%20Yar%20town%2C%20in%20Donetsk%20region%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20Thursday%2C%20May%2015%2C%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683d6dc66ffb6822ec61de8c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223781%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkraine%20and%20Russia%20are%20using%20various%20types%20of%20drones%20to%20carry%20out%20strike%20and%20reconnaissance%20missions.%3Cp%3EOleg%20Petrasiuk%2FUkraine's%2024th%20Mechanized%20Brigade%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20the%20early%20phase%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20general%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20trying%20to%20follow%20everything%20that%20is%20happening%20behind%20the%20border%2C%20like%20what%20the%20Ukrainians%20are%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20difficult%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmy-secretary-us-cant-make-expensive-weapons-vulnerable-cheap-drones-2025-5%5C%22%20target%