nt-microsoft-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enow-iconic%2C%20sweat-drenched%20%26quot%3BDevelopers!%20Developers!%20Developers!%26quot%3B%20chant%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20an%20early%202000s%20conference%2C%20said%20he%20initially%20tried%20to%20stay%20involved%2C%20not%20operationally%20but%20as%20an%20ultra-engaged%20investor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20read%20everything%2C%20attended%20conferences%20and%20even%20went%20to%20a%20shareholder%20meeting%20where%2C%20by%20his%20own%20account%2C%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bkind%20of%20a%20dick.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20too%20emotionally%20attached%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20control%20anything%20anymore%2C%20so%20it's%20hard.%20You%20don't%20want%20to%20stay%20quite%20that%20emotionally%20attached%20because%20it's%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20I%20got%20to%20get%20back%20in%20and%20fix%20everything.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20year%2C%20Ballmer%20said%20he%20slowly%20worked%20on%20letting%20go.%20But%20his%20emotional%20attachment%20deepened%20when%20he%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20philanthropist%20Connie%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESnyder%2C%20began%20ramping%20up%20their%20philanthropy%2C%20eventually%20prompting%20him%20to%20consider%20selling%20all%20his%20Microsoft%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20only%20thought%20process%20was%20emotional%20detachment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20just%20before%20he%20could%20hit%20the%20sell%20button%2C%20he%20said%20a%20former%20Microsoft%20colleague%20working%20with%20him%20in%20finance%20stopped%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20said%2C%20'You%20can't%20sell.%20This%20is%20going%20to%20be%20worth%20a%20lot%20more'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20said%2C%20'Look%2C%20my%20loyalty%20trumps%20my%20emotional%20attachment%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20held%20on%20to%20his%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Ballmer%20said%20he's%20found%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20going%20to%20be%20loyal%20and%20emotionally%20detached%20enough%20for%20this%20to%20be%20okay%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20no%20longer%20obsesses%20over%20the%20stock's%20highs%20or%20lows%20and%20has%20peace%20of%20mind%20knowing%20the%20foundation%20his%20wife%20and%20he%20built%20is%20thriving%20regardless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-ballmer-reveals-why-leaving-microsoft-was-best-decision-yet-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748869301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683d93c16ffb6822ec61dfab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-ballmer-reveals-why-leaving-microsoft-was-best-decision-yet-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Steve%20Ballmer%2C%20ex-CEO%20of%20Microsoft%2C%20described%20his%20emotional%20detachment%20process%20from%20the%20company%20and%20how%20it%20influenced%20his%20philanthropic%20endeavors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tspirlet%40insider.com%20(Thibault%20Spirlet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A175%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-ballmer-reveals-why-leaving-microsoft-was-best-decision-yet-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Italy's%20Mount%20Etna%20erupts%20violently%2C%20sending%20massive%20ash%20plumes%20into%20sky%20as%20people%20run%20for%20safety%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748869279000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-121573761%2Cimgsize-979555.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwatch-italys-mount-etna-erupts-violently-sending-massive-ash-plumes-into-sky-as-people-run-for-safety%2Farticleshow%2F121573706.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%