Cp%3EOne%20mistake%20people%20make%20is%20assuming%20that%20a%20company's%20sales%20equal%20personal%20wealth.%20I'm%20clear%20about%20the%20difference%20between%20my%20company's%20profits%20and%20my%20net%20worth%20(which%20I%20prefer%20to%20keep%20private).%20I%20live%20based%20on%20the%20salary%20I'm%20paid%20by%20Salt.XO%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmultimillionaire-balance-frugality-treating-kids-indulging-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereinvest%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20profits%20into%20the%20team%20and%20the%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20my%20kids%20live%20very%20differently%20from%20the%20way%20I%20was%20raised.%20They%20have%20pretty%20much%20everything%20they%20need%3A%20clothes%2C%20a%20nanny%2C%20and%20fun%20outings.%20We're%20in%20Florida%2C%20and%20a%20trip%20to%20the%20amusement%20parks%20was%20a%20huge%20deal%20for%20me%20as%20a%20kid.%20But%20for%20my%20son%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-orlando-how-to-save-money-at-parks-family-trip%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egoing%20to%20Universal%3C%2Fa%3E%20feels%20like%20a%20casual%20Friday%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221e19a0f4-56d9-496e-b97d-dcc5b7b95de9%5C%22%3EI%20don't%20want%20my%20sons%20to%20have%20instant%20gratification%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20my%20oldest%20is%20in%20kindergarten%2C%20I'm%20working%20hard%20to%20help%20him%20understand%20money%20and%20the%20work%20that's%20tied%20to%20it.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20raise%20my%20boys%20with%20a%20lack%20mentality%2C%20but%20I%20want%20them%20to%20understand%20the%20reality%20of%20money%2C%20access%2C%20and%20privilege.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20emphasize%20that%2C%20I've%20started%20pulling%20back%20on%20the%20things%20my%20sons%20have%20access%20to.%20I%20don't%20want%20them%20to%20always%20have%20instant%20gratification.%20I%20know%20from%20my%20childhood%20that%20waiting%20and%20saving%20for%20things%20made%20me%20appreciate%20them%20more%2C%20and%20that%20made%20me%20who%20I%20am%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2267f3d7c8-25bb-4776-b272-aeee63665ad4%5C%22%3EI%20tell%20my%20son%20how%20much%20I'm%20spending%20in%20stores%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20talk%20with%20my%20son%20about%20money%2C%20as%20if%20he%20were%20much%20older%20than%205.%20When%20we%20go%20to%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20I%20read%20the%20total%20to%20him.%20Then%2C%20we%20talk%20about%20what%20spending%20%24300%20on%20something%20means.%20I%20discuss%20how%20many%20hours%20or%20days%20I%20need%20to%20work%20to%20bring%20that%20money%20into%20our%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20usually%20let%20him%20pick%20one%20snack%20and%20one%20toy%20when%20we're%20shopping.%20But%20that's%20it.%20Limiting%20what%20he%20can%20have%20helps%20him%20understand%20that%20money%20doesn't%20grow%20on%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2266515f54-d70a-4271-8870-269eba600da9%5C%22%3EWe%20use%20a%20physical%20piggy%20bank%20so%20my%20son%20can%20see%20his%20savings%20grow%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son's%20dad%20and%20I%20have%20been%20saving%20for%20him%20since%20he%20was%20an%20infant.%20We%20do%20it%20with%20a%20physical%20piggy%20bank%2C%20which%20is%20easy%20for%20him%20to%20see%20and%20understand.%20He%20contributes%20the%20allowance%20he%20gets%20from%20helping%20with%20the%20dog%20and%20the%20gifts%20people%20give%20him.%20Each%20time%20he%20fills%20the%20piggy%20bank%2C%20we%20get%20a%20bigger%20container.%20Right%20now%2C%20his%20bank%20is%20a%20rocket%20ship%2C%20but%20by%20the%20time%20he's%2018%2C%20I%20hope%20it's%20a%20giant%20tote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20helped%20my%20son%20become%20more%20conscious%20about%20saving.%20Sometimes%2C%20on%20those%20trips%20to%20the%20store%2C%20I'll%20tell%20him%20I'll%20give%20him%20the%20money%20for%20a%20toy%2C%20and%20he%20can%20choose%20to%20spend%20it%20or%20save%20it.%20Often%2C%20the%20money%20ends%20up%20in%20his%20piggy%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224a8014db-6395-4216-94e4-aa84270250d1%5C%22%3EI%20have%20big%20financial%20dreams%20for%20myself%2C%20too%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20never%20taught%20how%20to%20invest%20and%20grow%20money.%20I%20had%20to%20learn%20on%20my%20own%2C%20sometimes%20through%20mistakes.%20So%2C%20I%20plan%20to%20teach%20the%20boys%20about%20investing%2C%20planning%20for%20retirement%2C%20and%20weighing%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20of%20taking%20out%20a%20loan%20versus%20paying%20cash%20for%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20have%20big%20financial%20dreams%20myself.%20Once%2C%20being%20a%20millionaire%20seemed%20like%20a%20pipe%20dream.%20Now%2C%20I%20want%20to%20be%20a%20billionaire.%20I%20don't%20get%20envious%20when%20I%20see%20people%20who%20are%20ahead%20of%20me.%20Instead%2C%20I%20think%3A%20What%20do%20I%20need%20to%20do%20to%20get%20there%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmultimillionaire-believes-that-teaching-kids-about-money-is-important-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748867521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68078b42a466d2b74ab3c457%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmultimillionaire-believes-that-teaching-kids-about-money-is-important-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jhalesa%20Seymour%20founded%20Salt.XO%20while%20in%20college%20and%20now%20it's%20a%20multimillion%20dollar%20company.%20She%20talks%20to%20her%205-year-old%20about%20money%20and%20saving.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Burch)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A56%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmultimillionaire-believes-that-teaching-kids-about-money-is-important-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UN%2C%20Iran%2C%20Egypt%20meet%20in%20Cairo%20to%20discuss%20Tehran's%20nuclear%20programme%22%2C%22conten