n%20upon%20which%20Gone%20Fishing%20Cottages%20was%20built.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20before%20we%20started%20running%20a%20home%2C%20we%20made%20sure%20the%20sewage%20and%20waste%20disposal%20were%20sorted%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20A%20biodigester%2C%20an%20advanced%20system%20for%20natural%20sewage%20treatment%2C%20was%20one%20of%20their%20first%20major%20investments.%20Compost%20pits%20%E2%80%94%20eight%20in%20total%20%E2%80%94%20were%20dug%20across%20the%20property.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlastic%20usage%20has%20been%20consciously%20minimised%20at%20every%20step.%20Single-use%20plastics%20like%20Maggi%20and%20chips%20packets%20are%20quite%20a%20nuisance%2C%20to%20be%20honest.%20We%20tried%20to%20make%20a%20conscious%20decision%20that%20there%20should%20be%20no%20plastic%20that%20we%20are%20providing%20on%20top%20of%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dimple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T173148.780-1748520121.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20garden%20area%20at%20the%20Gone%20Fishing%20cottages%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T173148.780-1748520121.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T173148.780-1748520121-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T173148.780-1748520121-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T173148.780-1748520121-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29