al%2C%20not%20just%20used%20traditionally%2C%20but%20innovatively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20a%20technique%20called%20rat-trap%20bond%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gauri%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20involves%20laying%20bricks%20with%20a%20vertical%20gap%2C%20which%20reduces%20the%20number%20of%20bricks%20used%20and%20adds%20thermal%20insulation.%20It%E2%80%99s%20cost-effective%20and%20perfect%20for%20our%20climate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T121609.552-1748501177.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20partition%20in%20the%20ground%20floor%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T121609.552-1748501177.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T121609.552-1748501177-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T121609.552-1748501177-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T121609.552-1748501177-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T121609.552-1748501177-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-440874%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20rat-trap%20bond%20technique%20reduces%20the%20usage%20of%20bricks%20while%20providing%20a%20good%20pattern.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20bricks%20were%20also%20used%20to%20create%20brick%20%3Cem%3Ejaalis%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20perforated%20screens%20that%20allow%20light%20and%20