0the%20school%E2%80%99s%20mid-day%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20called%20biophilic%20architecture%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gauri.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20children%20to%20feel%20connected%20to%20nature%2C%20to%20see%20themselves%20as%20part%20of%20an%20ecosystem.%20When%20they%20care%20for%20a%20plant%20or%20harvest%20vegetables%20they%E2%80%99ve%20grown%2C%20it%20changes%20the%20way%20they%20relate%20to%20the%20space.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECross-ventilation%2C%20north-facing%20skylights%2C%20and%20sloped%20roofs%20further%20ensured%20that%20the%20school%20remained%20thermally%20comfortable%20and%20naturally%20lit%20year-round.%20These%20passive%20design%20strategies%20eliminated%20the%20need%20for%20artificial%20cooling%20or%20lighting%20during%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilt%20smart%20and%20affordable%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20astonishing%20aspect%20of%20the%20Saraswati%20Vidyalaya%20rebuild%20was%20its%20cost-efficiency.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20managed%20to%20keep%20the%20cost%20at%20just%20Rs%201%2C200%20per%20square%20foot%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tejesh.%C2%A0%20We%20achieved%20this%20through%20smart%20material%20choices%2C%20local%20labour%2C%20and%20reusing%20what%20others%20might%20discard.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T121748.468-1748501756.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20pattern%20on%20the%20river%20replicated%20on%20the%20floor%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T121748.468-1748501756.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T121748.468-1748501756-300x157.jpg%20300w