E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20new%20design%20of%20the%20school%20has%20brought%20in%20confidence%20among%20the%20students%20and%20teachers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20transformation%20has%20also%20been%20officially%20recognised.%20Saraswati%20Vidyalaya%20recently%20received%20third%20prize%20in%20a%20statewide%20competition%20organised%20under%20the%20Chief%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20school%20excellence%20initiative%2C%20winning%20Rs%201%20lakh%20and%20earning%20acclaim%20for%20both%20its%20educational%20and%20architectural%20merit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%E2%80%99s%20success%20was%20made%20possible%20by%20a%20network%20of%20generous%20donors%20and%20empathetic%20institutions.%20Learning%20Space%20Foundation%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20mobilising%20support%20and%20linking%20the%20school%20with%20organisations%20like%20Universal%20General%20Insurance%20Company%2C%20which%20contributed%20Rs%209%20lakh%20to%20kickstart%20construction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Jamnabai%20Narsee%20School%20in%20Mumbai%20stepped%20in%20with%20funding%2C%20furniture%2C%20and%20by%20fostering%20beautiful%20exchange%20of%20ideas%20and%20values.%20Their%20students%20raised%20funds%20and%20visited%20Kelthan%20to%20understand%20rural%20education%20realities%20better%2C%20bridging%20a%20rarely%20crossed%20gap%20between%20urban%20and%20rural%20worlds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20like%20a%20barter%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gauri.%20%E2%80%9CCity%20students%20gave%20their%20time%20and%20resources%2C%20and%20in%20return%2C%20they%20received%20a%20grounded%2C%20eye-opening%20experience.%20It%20was%20about%20connecting%20the%20dots%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20worked.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPhase%202%20and%20beyond%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%2C%20however%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20over.%20unTAG%20has%20already%20completed%20the%20design%20for%20Phase